1911 Guelph Maple Leafs Roster

1911 Guelph Maple Leafs Statistics

The Guelph Maple Leafs of the Canadian League ended the 1911 season with a record of 45 wins and 62 losses, finishing fifth in the CL.

Abbie Johnson, William Lane and Hugh Shannon served as manager.
